    <item>
      <title>香港首次推出加密货币 ETF</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-04-30/hong-kong-debuts-crypto-etfs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[香港证券交易所和华夏基金等多家基金管理公司周二对香港加密货币 ETF 的推出表示欢迎。对新一批现货比特币和以太币产品的需求水平将表明香港推动严格监管的数字资产中心是否正在获得牵引力。 （来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-04-30/hong-kong-debuts-crypto-etfs</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 30 Apr 2024 08:33:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国最高领导人暗示房地产支持和降息</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-30/china-s-top-leaders-will-study-steps-to-digest-housing-stockpile</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国执政党共产党誓言要研究解决国内过剩住房库存问题的措施，这表明将加大对长期房地产危机的帮助，并暗示可能下调利率。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-30/china-s-top-leaders-will-study-steps-to-digest-housing-stockpile</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 30 Apr 2024 07:15:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国将于7月召开推迟举行的党的改革会议</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-30/china-to-hold-delayed-party-conclave-focusing-on-reform-in-july</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国国家主席习近平将于 7 月召集党内高级官员召开闭门会议，届时将密切关注世界第二大经济体长期改革的迹象。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-30/china-to-hold-delayed-party-conclave-focusing-on-reform-in-july</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 30 Apr 2024 07:05:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
