      <title>欧元区加速走出衰退，但通胀却很棘手</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-30/europe-gdp-latest-france-grows-in-hope-region-out-of-recession</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧元区摆脱了衰退，尽管近期通胀回落陷入停滞，但四大经济体的增长速度远超预期。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-30/europe-gdp-latest-france-grows-in-hope-region-out-of-recession</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 30 Apr 2024 05:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
